<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٦٩٦ - أَخْبَرَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5187">‌قُتَيْبَةُ </a>،<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2478">‌سُفْيَانُ </a>، عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/4620">‌عَمَّارٍ الدُّهْنِيِّ </a>،<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗٣٦⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3745">‌أَبِي سَلَمَةَ </a>، عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6741">‌أُمِّ سَلَمَةَ </a>أَنَّ النَّبِيَّ صَلَّى اللهُ عَلَيْهِ وَسَلَّمَ قَالَ: <span class="c2">«إِنَّ قَوَائِمَ مِنْبَرِي هَذَا رَوَاتِبُ فِي الْجَنَّةِ»</span>.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>